5
00:00:38,320 --> 00:00:40,960
I don't feel so good.

6
00:00:40,970 --> 00:00:43,910
The doctor said to keep
taking your chemo pills.

7
00:00:44,440 --> 00:00:46,530
Here. Take one of these.

8
00:00:49,500 --> 00:00:51,590
Hang on, Nicky.

9
00:00:53,040 --> 00:00:56,280
If we get up over the
ridge, we'll be safe.

10
00:00:58,350 --> 00:01:00,600
Come on...

11
00:01:01,900 --> 00:01:04,210
Dad! Dad!

12
