We did it, Nicky.

16
00:01:27,380 --> 00:01:30,440
No way the floodwater
will reach this high.

17
00:01:34,990 --> 00:01:36,790
Dad?

18
00:01:38,300 --> 00:01:40,960
If I'm gonna die...

19
00:01:42,760 --> 00:01:45,350
who's gonna take care of you?

20
00:01:45,360 --> 00:01:48,540
Come here, buddy. Come here.

21
00:01:50,370 --> 00:01:52,780
You're okay.

