24
00:02:21,480 --> 00:02:25,390
Listen to that crowd go crazy! Yeah!

25
00:02:26,600 --> 00:02:28,290
Hey, hold on, Nicky.

26
00:02:28,310 --> 00:02:30,040
Why don't you head inside, son?

27
00:02:30,450 --> 00:02:32,580
Okay.

28
00:02:41,790 --> 00:02:42,880
Dr. Reeves.

29
00:02:42,910 --> 00:02:44,950
Nicky was scheduled
for surgery a week ago.

30
00:02:44,960 --> 00:02:47,290
Why haven't you returned our calls?

31
00:02:47,300 --> 00:02:49,520
'Cause Nicky doesn't
need surgery. He's fine.

32
00:02:49,530 --> 00:02:52,090
Daniel, he has a tumor on his kidney.

33
00:02:52,110 --> 00:02:55,070
Without surgery, he is going to die.

34
00:02:55,080 --> 00:02:57,160
Where's your faith, Dr. Reeves?

35
00:02:57,190 --> 00:02:59,510
You know I'm not going
to let you take him.

36
00:03:02,160 --> 00:03:03,910
Officer?

37
00:03:04,660 --> 00:03:07,510
Mr. Harris, we have a court
order appeal by Child Services.

38
00:03:07,520 --> 00:03:09,810
They're forcing us to act in the
best interest of Nicholas Harris.

39
00:03:09,840 --> 00:03:12,090
Lave my son alone!

40
00:03:12,100 --> 00:03:13,620
Let go of my son!

41
00:03:13,640 --> 00:03:15,610
He'll die if we don't
get him to a hospital.

42
00:03:15,630 --> 00:03:17,390
Does it look like he's gonna die to you?

43
00:03:17,410 --> 00:03:18,730
Dad, it's okay.

44
00:03:18,750 --> 00:03:21,370
- Nicky!
- It's okay.

45
00:03:22,130 --> 00:03:24,270
Dr. Reeves?

46
00:03:24,280 --> 00:03:27,040
Do you believe in miracles?

47
00:03:27,980 --> 00:03:29,400
You will.

48
